<br>
make charge as is a class defineing skill on a 2 min timer replace flurry by makeing charge get better as the light tank progresses, charge one = just sprint speed, charge two = sprint up and attack with a flurry, charge 3 = sprint forward at a speed faster than normal sprint and hit with a stronger flurry. (something to that effect)<br>
